ired by Russia in 17th-18th centuries from Lithuania/Poland","tier":"secondary","source":"ICOW Colonial History 1.1"},{"from":"RUS","to":"UZB","colonizer":"RUS","colonized":"UZB","empire":"Russia / USSR","start_year":null,"end_year":1991,"ind_violent":false,"ind_type":3,"notes":"Gradually occupied by Russia over 19th century","tier":"secondary","source":"ICOW Colonial History 1.1"},{"from":"TUR","to":"ALB","colonizer":"TUR","colonized":"ALB","empire":"Ottoman Empire","start_year":null,"end_year":1913,"ind_violent":true,"ind_type":2,"notes":"COW system interrupted 4/1939-11/1944 (Ital/Ger occup); terr chg also codes 1945 return","tier":"secondary","source":"ICOW Colonial History 1.1"},{"from":"TUR","to":"ARM","colonizer":"TUR","colonized":"ARM","empire":"Ottoman Empire","start_year":null,"end_year":1991,"ind_violent":false,"ind_type":3,"notes":"Terr chg also includes 1918 violent secession (but not system entry); previously under Ottoman/Persian rule; parts ceded to Russia in 1828-89 and 1878","tier":"secondary","source":"ICOW Colonial History 1.1"},{"from":"TUR","to":"BGR","colonizer":"TUR","colonized":"BGR","empire":"Ottoman Empire","start_year":null,"end_year":1878,"ind_violent":true,"ind_type":2,"notes":null,"tier":"secondary","source":"ICOW Colonial History 1.1"},{"from":"TUR","to":"BIH","colonizer":"TUR","colonized":"BIH","empire":"Ottoman Empire","start_year":null,"end_year":1992,"ind_violent":true,"ind_type":3,"notes":"Acquired by Austria from Turkey in 1878 Treaty of Berlin","tier":"secondary","source":"ICOW Colonial History 1.1"},{"from":"TUR","to":"EGY","colonizer":"TUR","colonized":"EGY","empire":"Ottoman Empire","start_year":null,"end_year":1831,"ind_violent":false,"ind_type":2,"notes":"Also occupied by British from 1882-1922 (rejoins COW 5/1937 & G/W 2/1922)","tier":"secondary","source":"ICOW Colonial History 1.1"},{"from":"TUR","to":"GRC","colonizer":"TUR","colonized":"GRC","empire":"Ottoman Empire","start_year":null,"end_year":1829,"ind_violent":true,